{{Infobox Museum|name=戰爭兒童博物館|image=|caption=|map_type=|coordinates={{Coord|43|51|42|N|18|25|42|E|region:BH_type:landmark|display=inline,title}}|established=2017|dissolved=|location=Logavina 32, [[Sarajevo|Sarajevo]]|type=[[歷史博物館|歷史博物館]]|visitors=|founder=亞斯明科．哈利洛維奇（Jasminko Halilovic）|publictransit=|website=[http://museum.warchildhood.com/ WCM]}}'''戰爭兒童博物館'''（[[波士尼亞語|波士尼亞語]]：''Muzej ratnog djetinjstva''，英語：War Childhood Museum）是一座歷史博物館，位於[[波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納聯邦|波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納聯邦]]首都[[塞拉耶佛|塞拉耶佛]]，於2017年1月開幕。透過各項物品、影片證據及口述歷史的呈現，該館展出歷經[[波士尼亞戰爭|波士尼亞戰爭]]孩童的經歷。 

此計畫始於2010年，塞拉耶佛企業家、行動主義者兼「戰爭兒童」亞斯明科．哈利洛維奇（Jasminko Halilovic）透過一個網路平台向那些於波士尼亞戰爭時曾是孩童的年輕人蒐集回憶錄片段，超過1,000名年輕人貢獻他們的記憶，哈利洛維奇將這些回憶錄彙編成一本書並於2013年出版，此書隨後被翻譯成德文及日文。<ref>Sheehan, Dan (December 2015).[https://www.guernicamag.com/children-of-war "Jasminko Halilovic: Children of War"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.guernicamag.com/children-of-war |date=20210130103737 }}. Guernica Magazine. Retrieved 5 February 2017.</ref>

當哈利洛維奇開始和那些貢獻回憶的年輕人們聯繫，他發現許多前「戰爭兒童」都還留著一些特定物品，讓他們能夠連結記憶。<ref>Toe, Rodolfo (May 11, 2016). [http://www.balkaninsight.com/en/article/bosnian-museum-preserves-war-childhood-memories-05-11-2016 "Sarajevo Museum to Preserve Wartime Childhood Memories"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.balkaninsight.com/en/article/bosnian-museum-preserves-war-childhood-memories-05-11-2016 |date=20170921091354 }}. Balkan Transitional Justice. Balkan Insight.</ref>隨後，哈利洛維奇便開始和另一群年輕專家合作，開發博物館收藏，最終收集了超過3,000項物品和超過60個口述歷史證詞。<ref>Rose, Eleanor (January 1, 2017). [http://www.balkaninsight.com/en/article/bosnia-s-war-childhood-museum-finally-opens-01-30-2017 "Bosnia's War Childhood Museum Finally Opens"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.balkaninsight.com/en/article/bosnia-s-war-childhood-museum-finally-opens-01-30-2017 |date=20170920110610 }}. Balkan Transitional Justice. Balkan Insight. Retrieved 5 February 2017.</ref>

2016年5月，戰爭兒童博物館於[[Historical_Museum_of_Bosnia_and_Herzegovina|波赫聯邦歷史博物館]]<ref>Toe, Rodolfo. [http://www.balkaninsight.com/en/article/bosnian-museum-preserves-war-childhood-memories-05-11-2016 "Sarajevo Museum to Preserve Wartime Childhood Memories"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.balkaninsight.com/en/article/bosnian-museum-preserves-war-childhood-memories-05-11-2016 |date=20170921091354 }}. Balkan Transitional Justice. Balkan Insight. Retrieved 5 February 2017.</ref>舉行首次臨時展覽，隨後並於[[澤尼察|澤尼察]]（Zenica）與[[維索科|維索科]]（Visoko）<ref>Ruvic, Dado (July 8, 2016). [http://in.reuters.com/article/bosnia-museum-idINKCN0ZO0ZV "Bosnian museum of wartime childhood helps heal trauma"] {{Wayback|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/bosnia-museum-idINKCN0ZO0ZV |date=20181005153811 }}. Reuters. Retrieved 5 February 2017.</ref>舉辦更多展覽。2017年1月，戰爭兒童博物館的常設展覽於塞拉耶佛的洛加維納街（Logavina Street）開幕。

該館館藏包含日記、玩具、照片、衣物等由戰爭倖存者捐獻的各類物品，所有物品皆與捐獻者的自傳回憶錄共同呈現<ref>Halilovic, Jasminko. War Childhood Museum http://museum.warchildhood.com.</ref>，除了參觀展品，訪客可以收聽證詞並閱讀口述歷史的訪談片段。<ref>Rose, Eleanor (January 30, 2017). [http://www.balkaninsight.com/en/article/bosnia-s-war-childhood-museum-finally-opens-01-30-2017 "Bosnia's War Childhood Museum Finally Opens"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.balkaninsight.com/en/article/bosnia-s-war-childhood-museum-finally-opens-01-30-2017 |date=20170920110610 }}. Balkan Transitional Justice. Retrieved 5 February 2017.</ref>

